<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-29-0635 </DOCNO><TEXT>The steps taken to select and implement digital control systems for threeRefineries owned by KNPC are explained. Two new refineries are designedto be controlled by a digital control system, and one is being revampedfrom conventional analog to digital. Revamping procedures are also describedfrom the start of the project to the commissioning stage.</TEXT></DOC>